{"day":14,"topic":{"title":"Use of Let's","emoji":"🎯","cefr":"A2","difficulty":"elementary","type":"grammar"},"content":{"explanation":"\n**Let's — Suggestion & Invitation:**\n\n\"Let's\" = \"Let us\" ka short form\nUse hota hai jab hum kisi ko kuch karne ki **suggestion** dete hain.\n\n🇮🇳 चलो बाहर जाते हैं।\n🇬🇧 **Let's** go outside.\n\n🇮🇳 चलो इसके बारे में बात करते हैं।\n🇬🇧 **Let's** talk about this.\n\n**Patterns:**\n- Let's + base verb (positive suggestion)\n- Let's not + base verb (negative suggestion)\n- Shall we + base verb? (question form)\n  ","rules":["Let's = Let us (always for group/both people)","Let's + base verb: Let's go, Let's eat, Let's start","Let's not + verb: Let's not waste time","Shall we + verb? = Let's ke question form","Response: Yes, let's! / No, let's not. / Good idea!","Don't confuse: Let's (suggestion) vs Let (permission)"],"memoryTrick":"**Let's = चलो!** — हिंदी में 'चलो' = English में 'Let's'. दोनों group suggestion के लिए हैं!","examples":[{"hindi":"चलो English practice करते हैं।","english":"Let's practice English.","type":"Let's + verb"},{"hindi":"चलो एक break लेते हैं।","english":"Let's take a break.","type":"Let's + verb"},{"hindi":"चलो इस topic को दोबारा नहीं करते।","english":"Let's not repeat this topic.","type":"Let's not + verb"},{"hindi":"क्या हम मिलकर lunch करें?","english":"Shall we have lunch together?","type":"Shall we? (question)"},{"hindi":"चलो इसे मिलकर solve करते हैं।","english":"Let's solve this together.","type":"Let's + verb"},{"hindi":"चलो पानी पीते हैं।","english":"Let's drink some water.","type":"Let's + noun phrase"}],"mistakes":[{"wrong":"Let's to go.","correct":"Let's go.","why":"Let's के बाद 'to' नहीं लगता"},{"wrong":"Let's going.","correct":"Let's go.","why":"Let's के बाद base verb (-ing नहीं)"},{"wrong":"Lets go! (no apostrophe)","correct":"Let's go!","why":"Apostrophe ज़रूरी है: Let's = Let us"},{"wrong":"Let's not to argue.","correct":"Let's not argue.","why":"Let's not के बाद base verb"}],"speakingTips":["रोज़ किसी को 'Let's + verb' वाला suggestion दो","Meeting में: 'Let's get started' / 'Let's move on'","Informally: 'Let's hang out sometime!' / 'Let's catch up soon!'"]},"vocabulary":[{"id":1,"word":"Together","hindi":"मिलकर","ipa":"","example":"Let's do this together."},{"id":2,"word":"Celebrate","hindi":"जश्न मनाना","ipa":"","example":"Let's celebrate your success!"},{"id":3,"word":"Collaborate","hindi":"सहयोग करना","ipa":"","example":"Let's collaborate on this project."},{"id":4,"word":"Discuss","hindi":"चर्चा करना","ipa":"","example":"Let's discuss the plan."},{"id":5,"word":"Organize","hindi":"व्यवस्थित करना","ipa":"","example":"Let's organize the event."},{"id":6,"word":"Plan","hindi":"योजना बनाना","ipa":"","example":"Let's plan the trip."},{"id":7,"word":"Begin","hindi":"शुरू करना","ipa":"","example":"Let's begin the lesson."},{"id":8,"word":"Focus","hindi":"ध्यान देना","ipa":"","example":"Let's focus on the main point."}],"practice":[{"id":"d14-001","hindi":"चलो बाहर जाते हैं।","english":"Let's go outside.","alternatives":["let's go out."],"hint":"Let's + base verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-002","hindi":"चलो खाना खाते हैं।","english":"Let's eat.","alternatives":["let's have food."],"hint":"Let's + eat","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-003","hindi":"चलो यह भूल जाते हैं।","english":"Let's forget about it.","alternatives":["let's move on."],"hint":"Let's + forget","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-004","hindi":"चलो मिलकर पढ़ते हैं।","english":"Let's study together.","alternatives":["let's read together."],"hint":"Let's + study together","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-005","hindi":"चलो फिल्म देखने चलते हैं।","english":"Let's go watch a movie.","alternatives":["let's catch a movie."],"hint":"Let's + go watch","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-006","hindi":"चलो शुरू करते हैं।","english":"Let's begin.","alternatives":["let's start."],"hint":"Let's + begin/start","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-007","hindi":"चलो plan बनाते हैं।","english":"Let's make a plan.","alternatives":["let's plan this."],"hint":"Let's + make a plan","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-008","hindi":"चलो celebrate करते हैं।","english":"Let's celebrate!","alternatives":["let's party!"],"hint":"Let's + celebrate","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-009","hindi":"चलो बाहर घूमने चलते हैं।","english":"Let's go for a walk.","alternatives":["let's take a walk."],"hint":"Let's go for a + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-010","hindi":"चलो इस topic को बंद करते हैं।","english":"Let's close this topic.","alternatives":["let's drop this topic."],"hint":"Let's + close","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-011","hindi":"चलो कॉफी पीते हैं।","english":"Let's have coffee.","alternatives":["let's get some coffee."],"hint":"Let's have + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-012","hindi":"चलो अभी नहीं जाते।","english":"Let's not go now.","alternatives":["let's stay a bit longer."],"hint":"Let's not + verb","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-013","hindi":"चलो इस पर बाद में बात करते हैं।","english":"Let's talk about this later.","alternatives":["let's discuss this later."],"hint":"Let's + talk about later","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-014","hindi":"चलो एक नई शुरुआत करते हैं।","english":"Let's make a fresh start.","alternatives":["let's begin again."],"hint":"Let's + make a fresh start","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-015","hindi":"चलो समय बर्बाद नहीं करते।","english":"Let's not waste time.","alternatives":["let's use our time well."],"hint":"Let's not + waste","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-016","hindi":"चलो साथ मिलकर काम करते हैं।","english":"Let's work together.","alternatives":["let's collaborate."],"hint":"Let's + work together","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-017","hindi":"चलो कुछ नया सीखते हैं।","english":"Let's learn something new.","alternatives":["let's try learning something new."],"hint":"Let's + learn something new","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-018","hindi":"चलो संगीत सुनते हैं।","english":"Let's listen to music.","alternatives":["let's play some music."],"hint":"Let's + listen to","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-019","hindi":"चलो इसे solve करते हैं।","english":"Let's solve this.","alternatives":["let's figure this out."],"hint":"Let's + solve","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-020","hindi":"चलो घर चलते हैं।","english":"Let's go home.","alternatives":["let's head home."],"hint":"Let's + go home","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-021","hindi":"चलो थोड़ा break लेते हैं।","english":"Let's take a short break.","alternatives":["let's pause for a moment."],"hint":"Let's take a + noun","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-022","hindi":"चलो इसे try करते हैं।","english":"Let's try this.","alternatives":["let's give this a go."],"hint":"Let's + try","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-023","hindi":"चलो एक साथ lunch करते हैं।","english":"Let's have lunch together.","alternatives":["let's grab lunch together."],"hint":"Let's have + noun + together","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-024","hindi":"चलो कल मिलते हैं।","english":"Let's meet tomorrow.","alternatives":["let's catch up tomorrow."],"hint":"Let's + meet + time","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-025","hindi":"चलो तेज़ चलते हैं।","english":"Let's walk faster.","alternatives":["let's speed up."],"hint":"Let's + verb + adverb","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-026","hindi":"चलो इस पर ध्यान देते हैं।","english":"Let's focus on this.","alternatives":["let's concentrate on this."],"hint":"Let's + focus on","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-027","hindi":"चलो कुछ interesting देखते हैं।","english":"Let's watch something interesting.","alternatives":["let's find something good to watch."],"hint":"Let's watch something + adjective","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-028","hindi":"चलो एक team बनाते हैं।","english":"Let's form a team.","alternatives":["let's build a team."],"hint":"Let's + form a team","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-029","hindi":"चलो किसी की मदद करते हैं।","english":"Let's help someone.","alternatives":["let's do something kind."],"hint":"Let's + help","explanation":""},{"id":"d14-030","hindi":"चलो इसे organize करते हैं।","english":"Let's organize this.","alternatives":["let's sort this out."],"hint":"Let's + organize","explanation":""}],"mockTest":[{"id":"d14-001-test","hindi":"चलो बाहर जाते हैं।","english":"Let's go outside.","alternatives":["let's go out."]},{"id":"d14-002-test","hindi":"चलो खाना खाते हैं।","english":"Let's eat.","alternatives":["let's have food."]},{"id":"d14-003-test","hindi":"चलो यह भूल जाते हैं।","english":"Let's forget about it.","alternatives":["let's move on."]},{"id":"d14-004-test","hindi":"चलो मिलकर पढ़ते हैं।","english":"Let's study together.","alternatives":["let's read together."]},{"id":"d14-005-test","hindi":"चलो फिल्म देखने चलते हैं।","english":"Let's go watch a movie.","alternatives":["let's catch a movie."]},{"id":"d14-006-test","hindi":"चलो शुरू करते हैं।","english":"Let's begin.","alternatives":["let's start."]},{"id":"d14-007-test","hindi":"चलो plan बनाते हैं।","english":"Let's make a plan.","alternatives":["let's plan this."]},{"id":"d14-008-test","hindi":"चलो celebrate करते हैं।","english":"Let's celebrate!","alternatives":["let's party!"]},{"id":"d14-009-test","hindi":"चलो बाहर घूमने चलते हैं।","english":"Let's go for a walk.","alternatives":["let's take a walk."]},{"id":"d14-010-test","hindi":"चलो इस topic को बंद करते हैं।","english":"Let's close this topic.","alternatives":["let's drop this topic."]},{"id":"d14-011-test","hindi":"चलो कॉफी पीते हैं।","english":"Let's have coffee.","alternatives":["let's get some coffee."]},{"id":"d14-012-test","hindi":"चलो अभी नहीं जाते।","english":"Let's not go now.","alternatives":["let's stay a bit longer."]},{"id":"d14-013-test","hindi":"चलो इस पर बाद में बात करते हैं।","english":"Let's talk about this later.","alternatives":["let's discuss this later."]},{"id":"d14-014-test","hindi":"चलो एक नई शुरुआत करते हैं।","english":"Let's make a fresh start.","alternatives":["let's begin again."]},{"id":"d14-015-test","hindi":"चलो समय बर्बाद नहीं करते।","english":"Let's not waste time.","alternatives":["let's use our time well."]},{"id":"d14-016-test","hindi":"चलो साथ मिलकर काम करते हैं।","english":"Let's work together.","alternatives":["let's collaborate."]},{"id":"d14-017-test","hindi":"चलो कुछ नया सीखते हैं।","english":"Let's learn something new.","alternatives":["let's try learning something new."]},{"id":"d14-018-test","hindi":"चलो संगीत सुनते हैं।","english":"Let's listen to music.","alternatives":["let's play some music."]},{"id":"d14-019-test","hindi":"चलो इसे solve करते हैं।","english":"Let's solve this.","alternatives":["let's figure this out."]},{"id":"d14-020-test","hindi":"चलो घर चलते हैं।","english":"Let's go home.","alternatives":["let's head home."]},{"id":"d14-021-test","hindi":"चलो थोड़ा break लेते हैं।","english":"Let's take a short break.","alternatives":["let's pause for a moment."]},{"id":"d14-022-test","hindi":"चलो इसे try करते हैं।","english":"Let's try this.","alternatives":["let's give this a go."]},{"id":"d14-023-test","hindi":"चलो एक साथ lunch करते हैं।","english":"Let's have lunch together.","alternatives":["let's grab lunch together."]},{"id":"d14-024-test","hindi":"चलो कल मिलते हैं।","english":"Let's meet tomorrow.","alternatives":["let's catch up tomorrow."]},{"id":"d14-025-test","hindi":"चलो तेज़ चलते हैं।","english":"Let's walk faster.","alternatives":["let's speed up."]},{"id":"d14-026-test","hindi":"चलो इस पर ध्यान देते हैं।","english":"Let's focus on this.","alternatives":["let's concentrate on this."]},{"id":"d14-027-test","hindi":"चलो कुछ interesting देखते हैं।","english":"Let's watch something interesting.","alternatives":["let's find something good to watch."]},{"id":"d14-028-test","hindi":"चलो एक team बनाते हैं।","english":"Let's form a team.","alternatives":["let's build a team."]},{"id":"d14-029-test","hindi":"चलो किसी की मदद करते हैं।","english":"Let's help someone.","alternatives":["let's do something kind."]},{"id":"d14-030-test","hindi":"चलो इसे organize करते हैं।","english":"Let's organize this.","alternatives":["let's sort this out."]}]}